headline: The Smartest Dividend King Stocks to Buy With $2,000 Right Now
summary: If you are a dividend lover, then you have very likely heard of Dividend Kings.  If you have $2,000 in cash (or any amount really) available to invest and you like the idea of owning reliable dividend stocks, you should be looking at Dividend Kings Nucor (NYSE: NUE), Black Hills (NYSE: BKH), and Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK) right now.
